casebody.data:
Kevin DAHLGREN, Applicant
v.
Loretta E. LYNCH, Attorney General, et al. No. 15A236. Supreme Court of the United States Aug. 28, 2015.

ORDER

RUTH BADER GINSBURG, Associate Justice of the Supreme Court of the United States.

UPON CONSIDERATION of the renewed application of counsel for the applicant,

IT IS ORDERED that the application for a stay is denied.
